                "name": "Negative Energy Ray",
                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "A telgrodradt can fire a sickly purple beam of negative energy from its eyes at a single target within 60 feet. If the telgrodradt successfully hits, the target takes 3d6 points of negative energy damage. This ray can also heal undead creatures. A telgrodradt can\u2019t target itself with this ability, but it can be healed by the negative energy rays of other telgrodradts."
